description:
Chat with Danielle about her post grad life, struggles of finding a friend “group”, and things she has learned since moving to New York. Hopefully, this episode will comfort other post grads or people who moved to a new city. Make sure to go follow @galsonthegopodcast Instagram to be involved in the question of the week!
